# Thermal printer udev rules
# Replace XXXX and YYYY with actual vendor/product IDs from `lsusb`
#
# To find your IDs:
#   1. Plug in the printer
#   2. Run: lsusb
#   3. Find the line for your printer (e.g. "Bus 001 Device 004: ID 0416:5011 ...")
#   4. Replace XXXX with the vendor ID and YYYY with the product ID
#
SUBSYSTEM=="usbmisc", ATTRS{idVendor}=="XXXX", ATTRS{idProduct}=="YYYY", \
  SYMLINK+="thermalprinter", TAG+="systemd", \
  ENV{SYSTEMD_WANTS}+="print-api.service", MODE="0660", GROUP="lp"
